Sentencas: Thin film solid oxide fuel cells, composed of thin coatings of 8 mol% Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ), thick substrates of infiltrated La0.8S0.2FeO3 (LSF)-YSZ cathodes and CuO-SDC (Ce0.85SM0.15O1.925)-ceria anodes, are fabricated using the conventional tape casting and infiltration methods.
Titulo: High-performance cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with copper cermet anodes

Sentencas: Infiltrated LSF-YSZ cathodes exhibit a much lower interfacial polarization resistance than (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.98)MnO3 (LSM)-YSZ cathodes due to the mixed ionic and electronic conducting behavior of LSF, especially at low operation temperatures.
Titulo: High-performance cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with copper cermet anodes

Sentencas: The single cell has shown good and stable performance in hydrogen and hydrocarbon fuels.
Titulo: High-performance cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with copper cermet anodes

Sentencas: Maximum power densities for hydrogen, propane, dodecane and low sulfur diesel at 800 degrees C are 0.62 W cm(-2), 0.40W cm(-2), 0.37W cm(-2) and 0.36 W cm(-2), respectively.
Titulo: High-performance cathode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with copper cermet anodes
